data.description: BEAUTIFUL PROPERTY!! BRAND NEW ROOF AND AC!!! If you like peaceful country living this home is perfect and priced under $175k! This 3 bed 2 full bath home is in phenomenal condition. The rooms are all huge and bathrooms as well. Large kitchen and living room with island and real wood burning fire place. Perfect for entertaining. The property itself is absolutely beautiful. Must see it in person to understand. Additional house pad already on property. Already has dual septic system, and septic lines, and electric box. Perfect for shop, 2nd home, or camper. Don't wait on this one, it will not last! Schedule a showing today!
